title: You Wish 1997 TGIF ABC Incomplete Collection
description:
This is an incomplete collection of episodes from the ABC sitcom You Wish. Its only season of 13 episodes aired in 1997 on ABC's TGIF lineup along with Teen Angel and Sabrina the Teenage Witch. I have searched the entire internet for evidence of this show and found only these recordings and few enough promo images to count on one hand.

If you have any of the missing episodes, please contact me at the email within the torrent's text file.


Episodes in this torrent:
01 Pilot
02 Jillions of Gillians
03 The Big Ride
04 Mind Games
06 Halloween
12 Bride and Prejudice
13 Gift of the Travi
